                 data-toggle="dropdown" aria-expanded="false"><span>Property Type</span></a>

              <div class="dropdown-menu" aria-labelledby="typeDropdown">
                <a class="dropdown-item" href="#"><span>DreamPlex 1 DreamPlex 1 DreamPlex 1 DreamPlex 1 DreamPlex 1 DreamPlex 1</span></a>
                <a class="dropdown-item" href="#"><span>DreamPlex 2</span></a>
